---
const APP_URL = 'https://ed-app-henna.vercel.app';
---

<section class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-600 to-primary-800">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white">
      Empieza hoy, es gratis
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-primary-200 max-w-xl mx-auto">
      Únete a la plataforma que conecta pacientes con los mejores especialistas. Sin costes ocultos, sin complicaciones.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
      <a
        href={`${APP_URL}/signin`}
        class="w-full sm:w-auto inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-base font-semibold text-primary-700 bg-white rounded-xl hover:bg-primary-50 transition-all shadow-lg shadow-black/20"
      >
        Soy paciente — Buscar doctor
      </a>
      <a
        href={`${APP_URL}/signin`}
        class="w-full sm:w-auto inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-base font-semibold text-white bg-white/10 rounded-xl border border-white/30 hover:bg-white/20 transition-all"
      >
        Soy doctor — Crear perfil
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
